<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو خَيْثَمَةَ:</span> ثنا سُفْيَانُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ عَمْرٌو:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#950000">"لَمَّا قَدِمَ مَكَّةَ يَعْنِي عُرْوَةَ قَالَ: "</span>ائْتُونِي فَتَلَقُّوا مِنِّي".<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>